---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import relax from '../images/illustrations/relax.png'
---

<section id="relax" class="py-6 md:py-14 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-36">
  <div
    class="rounded-3xl shadow-md md:shadow-lg border-[1px] border-secondary/20 flex flex-col items-center md:items-start md:flex-row justify-center py-6 sm:py-8 md:py-14 gap-6 sm:gap-10 md:gap-24 px-6 sm:px-8 md:px-10">
    <Image
      src={relax}
      alt="Relax"
      class="max-w-96 md:max-w-fit px-10 md:px-0"
    />
    <div class="font-medium flex flex-col gap-2 md:gap-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold font-main">
        Relax, We've Got This!
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-lg font-hightlight font-medium">
        At AcadAce, we take care of everything, so you can just relax. From
        projects to papers, we handle it all, ensuring your academic success
        without the stress. Trust us to deliver, while you focus on what matters
        most.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
